200
00:13:22,092 --> 00:13:23,628
Well, yeah.

201
00:13:24,637 --> 00:13:27,049
Okay. There you go.

202
00:13:33,437 --> 00:13:36,646
My mama always says
a lipstick makes you look like a lady,

203
00:13:36,732 --> 00:13:38,097
