they cover enough territory.

210
00:13:54,250 --> 00:13:56,241
But I made a promise to myself.

211
00:13:57,169 --> 00:14:00,252
Three inches above the knee.

212
00:14:01,382 --> 00:14:04,340
Otherwise, well, you know.

213
00:14:06,220 --> 00:14:08,587
I haven't worn a skirt since college.

214
00:14:09,557 --> 00:14:10,968
How old are you?

215
00:14:11,183 --> 00:14:12,594
Older than you.

216
00:14:14,144 --> 00:14:15,930
I always thought
it was something you grow out of.

217
00:14:16,021 --> 00:14:18,638
I've just never been very good
at the adult thing, I guess.

218
00:14:20,234 --> 00:14:21,941
Peter Pan of cutting.

219
00:14:22,945 --> 00:14:25,232
Yeah. I won't grow up, not me.

220
00:14:28,242 --> 00:14:31,701
