give him that big-eyed flirt

245
00:16:46,714 --> 00:16:48,330
you throwin' my way?

246
00:16:48,799 --> 00:16:50,540
What can I say? I love my job.

247
00:16:50,634 --> 00:16:52,500
Well, good luck with that.

248
00:16:52,594 --> 00:16:56,053
He's a hamster on a wheel
chasin' imaginary truckers.

249
00:16:56,223 --> 00:16:57,588
Mexican hog workers.

250
00:16:57,683 --> 00:16:59,299
