251
00:17:01,437 --> 00:17:02,893
No comment.

252
00:17:04,648 --> 00:17:07,106
Come on. The teeth, the bodies...

253
00:17:07,192 --> 00:17:09,149
It sure doesn't feel random, does it?

254
00:17:09,236 --> 00:17:11,898
And that dirt that you pulled off
of Bob Nash's tires...

255
00:17:11,989 --> 00:17:13,479
You trying to tell me
he's not a suspect?

256
00:17:13,574 --> 00:17:16,316
-I'm not trying to tell you anything.
-Okay, give me some insight.

257
00:17:16,410 --> 00:17:18,071
