617
00:42:23,123 --> 00:42:27,833
So let me guess.
You were like a preacher's daughter?

618
00:42:28,671 --> 00:42:30,378
Looks, money, and brains?

619
00:42:30,714 --> 00:42:34,924
Well, looks and money
will get you pretty far in this town.

620
00:42:36,178 --> 00:42:37,634
